rows.label: tlk45310111_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I guess it's true that going out
on a journey builds character.

rows.label: tlk45310111_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I mean, Rex, I still think of you as
a rookie salvager...

rows.label: tlk45310111_05_msg0003
rows.name:
But these days you're in a whole
different line of business, and doing
well for yourself as a Driver to boot.

rows.label: tlk45310111_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Wouldn't be surprised if you could
teach those Iira goons a thing or two.

rows.label: tlk45310111_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I feel like there's this strong bond
between you and your friends,
Blades and otherwise.

rows.label: tlk45310111_05_msg0006
rows.name:
All that business on the ancient ship
was just a horrible ordeal for me, but
I guess for you it was something more.
